### MindCare API - Testes com REST Client
### Use com VS Code Extension: REST Client
### Pressione Ctrl+Alt+R para executar a requisição

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@contentType = application/json

### ============================================================================
### 1. HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================================================

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ============================================================================
### 2. AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================================================

### Register - Patient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "patient1@example.com",
  "password": "senha123456",
  "role": "patient"
}

### Register - Professional
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "doctor1@example.com",
  "password": "senha123456",
  "role": "professional"
}

### Register - Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "senha123456",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Login - Patient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "patient1@example.com",
  "password": "senha123456"
}

### Login - Professional
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "doctor1@example.com",
  "password": "senha123456"
}

### ============================================================================
### 3. SPECIALTIES
### ============================================================================

### List Specialties (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/specialties

### Create Specialty (Admin) - Required token
### Copy token from login response and paste below
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/specialties
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...

{
  "name": "Cardiologia",
  "description": "Especialidade que estuda o coração e sistema cardiovascular"
}

### Create Specialty - Dermatologia
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/specialties
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Dermatologia",
  "description": "Especialidade que estuda a pele"
}

### Get Specialty by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/specialties/1

### ============================================================================
### 4. PROFESSIONALS
### ============================================================================

### Create Professional Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "crm": "123456/SP",
  "specialtyId": 1,
  "bio": "Cardiologista com 15 anos de experiência"
}

### Get My Professional Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/me
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

### List All Professionals (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals

### Get Professional by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/1

### Update My Professional Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/professionals/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "bio": "Cardiologista com 20 anos de experiência, especializado em arritmias"
}

### ============================================================================
### 5. PATIENTS
### ============================================================================

### Create Patient Profile
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/patients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-05-15T00:00:00Z",
  "phone": "11999999999",
  "address": "Rua Exemplo, 123 - São Paulo, SP"
}

### Get My Patient Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/me
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update My Patient Profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/patients/me
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "phone": "11988888888",
  "address": "Nova Rua, 456 - São Paulo, SP"
}

### ============================================================================
### 6. WORKING HOURS
### ============================================================================

### Create Working Hours (Professional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/working-hours
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "weekday": 1,
  "startTime": "09:00",
  "endTime": "17:00",
  "isActive": true
}

### Create Working Hours - Tuesday
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/working-hours
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "weekday": 2,
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "16:00",
  "isActive": true
}

### Get My Working Hours
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/working-hours/me
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Professional Working Hours
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/working-hours/professional/1

### Update Working Hours
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/working-hours/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "startTime": "08:00",
  "endTime": "18:00"
}

### ============================================================================
### 7. APPOINTMENTS
### ============================================================================

### Get Available Slots (Public)
### date format: YYYY-MM-DD
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/available-slots?professionalId=1&date=2026-05-22

### Create Appointment (Patient)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "professionalId": 1,
  "scheduledStartTime": "2026-05-22T14:00:00Z",
  "scheduledEndTime": "2026-05-22T14:30:00Z"
}

### Get My Appointments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/me
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get Appointment by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Cancel Appointment (Patient)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/1/cancel
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "cancellationReason": "Conflito com outro compromisso"
}

### ============================================================================
### 8. MEDICAL RECORDS
### ============================================================================

### Create Medical Record (Professional)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "patientId": 1,
  "appointmentId": 1,
  "recordText": "Paciente apresenta pressão elevada (150/90). Prescrever medicação antihipertensiva. Recomendado repouso e dieta com baixo sódio."
}

### Get Medical Record by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/1
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Get My Medical Records (Patient)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/me
Authorization: Bearer PATIENT_TOKEN_HERE

### Add Diagnosis
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/1/diagnoses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "cidCode": "I10",
  "description": "Hipertensão essencial (primária)"
}

### Add Diagnosis - Secondary
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/1/diagnoses
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "cidCode": "E78.5",
  "description": "Hiperlipidemia não especificada"
}

### Add Prescription
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/1/prescriptions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "medication": "Losartana",
  "dosage": "50mg",
  "instructions": "Tomar 1 comprimido ao amanhecer, 1 vez ao dia",
  "validity": "2026-06-22T00:00:00Z"
}

### Add Prescription - Atorvastatina
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/1/prescriptions
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer PROFESSIONAL_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "medication": "Atorvastatina",
  "dosage": "20mg",
  "instructions": "Tomar 1 comprimido à noite, 1 vez ao dia",
  "validity": "2026-06-22T00:00:00Z"
}

### Generate PDF of Medical Record
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/medical-records/1/pdf
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================================================
### 9. TELEMEDICINE
### ============================================================================

### Create Telemedicine Room
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telemedicine/rooms
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "appointmentId": 1
}

### Get Telemedicine Room Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/telemedicine/rooms/ABC12345
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Get Messages in Room
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/telemedicine/rooms/ABC12345/messages
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

### Update Room Status to Active
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/telemedicine/rooms/ABC12345/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "active"
}

### Update Room Status to Closed
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/telemedicine/rooms/ABC12345/status
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "closed"
}

### Send Message in Room
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/telemedicine/rooms/ABC12345/messages
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_HERE

{
  "content": "Olá, como você está se sentindo?"
}

### ============================================================================
### NOTES
### ============================================================================
### 1. Replace TOKEN_HERE com o token JWT da resposta de login
### 2. Qualquer campo obrigatório não preenchido causará erro 400
### 3. Rotas sem Authorization são públicas
### 4. Rate limit: 100 requisições por minuto
### 5. Cache de disponibilidade: 5 minutos
